--- a/THANKS
+++ b/THANKS
@@ -316,6 +316,7 @@ Olly Betts                  olly@survex.com
 Ossama Othman               ossama@debian.org
 Pallav Gupta                pallavgupta@gmail.com
 Paolo Bonzini               bonzini@gnu.org
+Patrice Dumas               pertusus@free.fr
 Patrick Tullmann            tullmann@cs.utah.edu
