 @acindex{FC_FREEFORM}
 @caindex fc_freeform
 
@@ -8314,8 +8314,8 @@ The result of this test, or @samp{none} or @samp{unknown}, is cached in
 the @code{ac_cv_fc_freeform} variable.
 @end defmac
 
-@defmac AC_FC_FIXEDFORM (@ovar{action-if-success}, @dvar{action-if-failure, @
